<!-- Default translations -->
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>Book I</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20221229T125021Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20221229T125021Z">
        <seg>Buku I</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From Diognetus,&lt;a0&gt;5&lt;/a0&gt; not to busy myself about trifling things, and not to give credit to what was said by miracle-workers and jugglers about incantations and the driving away of daemons and such things; and not to breed quails for fighting, nor to give myself up passionately to such things; and to endure freedom of speech; and to have become intimate with philosophy; and to have been a hearer, first of Bacchius, then of Tandasis and Marcianus; and to have written dialogues in my youth; and to have desired a plank bed and skin, and whatever else of the kind belongs to the Grecian discipline.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20230121T071349Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20230121T071349Z">
        <seg></seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From my governor, to be neither of the green nor of the blue party at the games in the Circus, nor a partisan either of the Parmularius or the Scutarius at the gladiators’ fights; from him too I learned endurance of labour, and to want little, and to work with my own hands, and not to meddle with other people’s affairs, and not to be ready to listen to slander.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20230121T070357Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20230121T070357Z">
        <seg>Dari gubernurku, agar tidak menjadi pendukung tim hijau atau tim biru pada pertandingan tertentu, juga tidak menjadi pendukung Parmularius dan Scutarius pada pertandingan gladiator; dari dia juga Aku belajar agar tabah dalam bekerja, dan punya sedikit keinginan, dan mengurusi urusanku sendiri, dan tidak ikut campur urusan orang lain, dan agar siap mendengar fitnah.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From my grandfather Verus&lt;a0&gt;1&lt;/a0&gt; I learned good morals and the government of my temper.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20221229T145817Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20221229T145817Z">
        <seg>Dari kakekku Verus&lt;a0&gt;1&lt;/a0&gt;Aku belajar moral baik dan pengelolaan emosiku.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From my great-grandfather,&lt;a0&gt;4&lt;/a0&gt; not to have frequented public schools, and to have had good teachers at home, and to know that on such things a man should spend liberally.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20230121T065914Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20230121T065914Z">
        <seg>Dari kakek buyutku,&lt;a0&gt;4&lt;/a0&gt; tidak sering mengunjungi sekolah-sekolah umum, dan untuk memiliki guru yang baik di rumah, dan untuk mengetahui bagaimana orang seharusnya menghabiskan waktu. </seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From my mother,&lt;a0&gt;3&lt;/a0&gt; piety and beneficence, and abstinence, not only from evil deeds, but even from evil thoughts; and further, simplicity in my way of living, far removed from the habits of the rich.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20230121T040834Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20230121T040834Z">
        <seg>Dari ibuku, &lt;a0&gt;3&lt;/a0&gt; kesalehan dan kedermawanan, dan berpantang, tidak hanya dari perilaku jahat, tapi juga dari pikiran buruk; dan lebih jauh lagi, kesederhanaan dalam gaya hidup yang jauh dari kebiasaan orang kaya.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu>
      <tuv lang="EN-US">
        <seg>From the reputation and remembrance of my father,&lt;a0&gt;2&lt;/a0&gt; modesty and a manly character.</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv lang="ID" changeid="apg" changedate="20230121T035334Z" creationid="apg" creationdate="20221229T145903Z">
        <seg>Melalui reputasi dan peringatan akan ayahku,&lt;a0&gt;2&lt;/a0&gt; kesederhanaan dan karakter berani. </seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
